media:group.media:title: Technoblade Never Dies
media:group.media:description:
In honor of the 9th anniversary of @Technoblade's channel, join us as we take a look at his lasting impact on his community through the phrase Technoblade Never Dies.


If you wish, donations can be made to the Sarcoma Foundation of America in his honor: https://www.curesarcoma.org/technoblade-tribute/
